<b>Transformation for NFV</b>
<br><br>
Network Function Virtualization has affected everything in the Telco 
industry over the past several years – both on the Carriers side as well
 as the Vendors angle and to everything in between – and all this has 
happened with only the beginnings of commercial deployments starting to 
make themselves known.  Follow my  personal blog series that builds on 
my own experience of creating what we all know today as NFV, with 
CloudBand and Alcatel-Lucent. I’ll discuss some of the areas that made 
us think differently and adjust the way we build a product, price it and
 discuss NFV strategy with our customers.
<br><br>
